# This domain's build products and secrets, none of it source:
#
#   .terraform/  Terraform's working directory: downloaded providers
#                and backend bookkeeping. The lock file
#                (.terraform.lock.hcl) is deliberately not ignored —
#                provider versions are pins like any other VERSION
#                file here.
#   identity/    the cluster's private keys and join token, minted by
#                the identity domain; never in history
#   image/       the assembled artifacts: the deployment layer, the
#                install image, and the disk image shipped to Linode
.terraform/
identity/
image/
